Trump to settle a CBS News lawsuit, and a fiery F.C.C. chair raises a poten=
tial new obstacle to the Skydance merger, David Ellison can only watch and =
plan for the day when=E2=80=94or maybe if=E2=80=94he finally takes control =
of the languishing studio.

